  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT305-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">kāppumikutikkaṇ tōḻi aṟattoṭu niṟpāḷākat taṉatu āṟṟāmai tōṉṟat talaimakaḷ
          taṉṉuḷḷē kūṟiyatu </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Uttered in herself by HER, so that her lack of strength
          appeared, while the confidante stood firm in duty, during an increase in guarding. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT305">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> kaṇṭara vanta kāma voḷḷeri</l>
          <l> yeṉpuṟa naliyiṉu mavaroṭu pēṇic</l>
          <l> ceṉṟunā muyaṅkaṟ karuṅkāṭ ciyamē</l>
          <l> vantañar kaḷaitalai yavarāṟ ṟalarē</l>
          <l> yuyttaṉar viṭāar pirittiṭai kaḷaiyār</l>
          <l> kuppaik kōḻit taṉippōr pōla</l>
          <l> viḷivāṅku viḷiyi ṉallatu</l>
          <l> kaḷaivō rilaiyā ṉuṟṟa nōyē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l rend="indent">Even though the bright flame of desire,</l>
          <l rend="indent7">that came as the eye brought [it] on,</l>
          <l rend="indent">afflicts [us] to the bone, having developed esteem towards him, </l>
          <l>we [are] a rare sight [difficult] to embrace. </l>
          <l>He is not able to come [and] remove [my] sorrow.</l>
          <l>No one is there to remove the pain I have,</l>
          <l>if not it perishes [then and] there, </l>
          <l rend="indent2">like cocks in a lone battle over a heap:</l>
          <l rend="indent4">he who has sent [them and] does not leave [them] off,</l>
          <l rend="indent4">doesn't separate [and] in between remove [them].</l>

        </lg>
      </div>
